          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 mb-2">üö® Critical Errors</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-1">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Out of stock alerts</li>
