              <li>‚Ä¢ Order delays</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Supplier unavailability</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Attention needed alerts</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 mb-2">‚úÖ Success Messages</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-1">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Item restocked confirmations</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Order placement success</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Bulk updates completed</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Reports generated</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Data synchronization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">‚ÑπÔ∏è Information</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-1">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Price updates</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ System maintenance</li>
